Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 08 of Mamma MRI
When I select the radio button 'Bone lesion'
Then 'Findings' dropdown is enabled
When I select 'Vertebral body' from Findings dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'TVB 1' checkbox is enabled
And 'TVB 2' checkbox is enabled
And 'TVB 3' checkbox is enabled
And 'TVB 4' checkbox is enabled
And 'TVB 5' checkbox is enabled
And 'TVB 6' checkbox is enabled
And 'TVB 7' checkbox is enabled
And 'TVB 8' checkbox is enabled
And 'TVB 9' checkbox is enabled
And 'TVB 10' checkbox is enabled
And 'TVB 11' checkbox is enabled
And 'TVB 12' checkbox is enabled
And 'Max. Diameter' input field is enabled
And 'Type of lesion' dropdown menu is enabled
When I select 'TVB 1' checkbox
And I select 'TVB 2' checkbox
And I select 'TVB 3' checkbox
And I select 'TVB 4' checkbox
And I select 'TVB 5' checkbox
And I select 'TVB 6' checkbox
And I select 'TVB 7' checkbox
And I select 'TVB 8' checkbox
And I select 'TVB 9' checkbox
And I select 'TVB 10' checkbox
And I select 'TVB 11' checkbox
And I select 'TVB 12' checkbox
And I enter '40' in 'Max. Diameter' input field
And I select 'Benign lesion' from 'Type of lesion' dropdown menu
And I click on 'Next page' button
Then I'm redirected to Page 09 of Mamma MRI.
